methods.add:
Adds a new series name to the namer.

:param name: (java.lang.Comparable) - new series name
:param plotInfo: io.deephaven.db.plot.errors.PlotInfo
methods.getNames:
Gets all the series names.
 
 The order of series in 3D-plots are determined by returned set.

:return: (java.util.List<java.lang.Comparable>) Set of seriesNames
methods.makeUnusedName:
Takes a potential series name and creates a unique name from it.  If the series would be new, the original series name is returned.

:param potentialName: (java.lang.String) - potential series name
:param plotInfo: io.deephaven.db.plot.errors.PlotInfo
:return: (java.lang.String) uniquified series name
methods.removeAll:
Remove all the specified series names.

:param names: (java.util.Collection<? extends java.lang.Comparable>) - series names to remove
